author: ian_dickinson
msg: Fixed problem with allValuesFrom and someValuesFrom restrictions, in
that they did not allow return values other than classes.  This is now
resolved, by adding a DataRange Java class to the API, and allowing
the restrictions to range over datatypes, data ranges, and classes.

author: chris-dollin
msg: More updates to ModelSpec; now FileModelMakers
get to specify their fileBase, and we're using RDFS models
